fullplot: A nurse from the Ukraine searches for a better life in the West, while an unemployed security guard from Austria heads East for the same reason.
plot: A nurse from the Ukraine searches for a better life in the West, while an unemployed security guard from Austria heads East for the same reason.
title: Import/Export

tomatoes.consensus: A grim and disturbing vision from Ulrich Seidl, makes for an uncomfortable and uncompromising picture of life, that is anything but comfy and pedestrian.
